info.name: WBBlades
info.description: 基于Mach-O解析技术的包大小占比分析、基于反汇编的Objective-C & Swift无用代码（冗余类）检测、点对点崩溃解析,支持big method /small method 解析 以及 iOS 15以上关于  dyld_chained_fixups的处理 (Technology app size analysis tool based on Mach-O, unused code (unused class) detection tool based on __text disassembly, point-to-point crash analysis tool based on dSYM or without dSYM.)
